    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding feels like a joke. how can you rebuild something when the core of it is just... gone? it feels more like a funeral than a transition. there's no \"new me\" coming, there's just the void where the old me used to be. it doesn't feel like a chance to be honest, it just feels like i'm waiting for something to end.",
